sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant CF as Consumer Frontend
    participant NX as Nginx (login-frontend)
    participant BFF as BFF Consumer
    participant FAS as FHIR API Service
    participant FDB as FHIR Database
    participant OE as openEHR System

    CF->>NX: GET /api/bff-consumer/patients/{id}<br/>(Bearer JWT)
    Note over NX: Proxy to bff-consumer
    NX->>BFF: Forward + Auth Header
    Note over BFF: Validate JWT &<br/>extract user info

    BFF->>FAS: GET Request (Patient ID)
    FAS->>FDB: Search by Patient ID
    Note over FDB: Locate patient record
    FDB-->>FAS: Personal Data & openEHR ID

    FAS->>OE: GET Medical Data (by openEHR ID)
    OE-->>FAS: Medical Data

    Note over FAS: Aggregate Personal<br/>& Medical Data
    FAS-->>BFF: Aggregated Payload
    BFF-->>NX: Aggregated Payload
    NX-->>CF: Aggregated Payload
